# PS-1: Requirement Validation
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: All feature requests

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Project Goals: Agreed-upon objectives that guide development priorities.

ENFORCE: Every feature must be validated against defined project goals before implementation begins.
PROHIBIT: Implementing unvalidated features.
ON VIOLATION: Halt feature execution → escalate to Product Owner or Product Governance Skill.
